Phan 1 - Phan tich: Y nghia cua executeUpdate()
Phuong thuc executeUpdate() la mot cong cu quan trong de kiem tra tinh thanh cong cua cau lenh SQL.

Gia tri tra ve: executeUpdate() tra ve mot so nguyen (int). So nay dai dien cho so luong dong (rows)
bi tac dong boi cau lenh SQL do.

Neu tra ve 1, 2, 10... nghia la co chung do dong da duoc cap nhat thanh cong.

Neu tra ve 0, nghia la khong co dong nao thoa man dieu kien WHERE. Trong truong hop cua ban,
 Bed_999 khong ton tai nen ket qua tra ve se la 0.

Cach phan hoi cho y ta: Chung ta se kiem tra bien int nay. Neu no bang 0, chung ta se in ra
thong bao: "Loi: Ma giuong khong ton tai trong he thong!" thay vi de im lang nhu ma nguon cu.